{"tid":2060447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三罷公投係反國安法嘅最後希望！","createTime":"2020-06-11T15:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T05:22:09.000Z","uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3f22772415ea1924cf1b19d5184f938d438c60","tid":2060447,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">事源</span></ins></span></div><br />\n國安法即將殺到，二百萬三罷聯合陣線23個工會於昨日(6/6)聯同中學生罷課平台召開記招，宣佈於14/6發起三罷公投。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pB9H73P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpB9H73P.jpg&h=4fbe41d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公投計劃內容</span></ins></span></div><br />\n公投將於14/6發起，當天會進行兩項公投。<br />\n第一項是罷工公投，投票對象係該23名工會嘅會員，由於對象只為工會會員，因此投票前必先加入公會；第二項是罷課公投，投票對象係全港中學生，會用實體票認證學生身份。時間地點稍後公佈！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJvTu7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJvTu7n.jpg&h=7675f177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公投程序</span>：</ins><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">若你是打工仔</span><br />\n1. 加入工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/305DVqj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F305DVqj&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0po9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=68cc57e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/305DVqj</a><br />\n2. 當日參與公投<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">若你是中學生</span><br />\n1. 帶同學生證明<br />\n2. 當日參與公投<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公投通過條件/目標</span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工公投</span><br />\n條件1: <br />\n6萬人參與公投，6成人支持罷工行動。<br />\n條件2: <br />\n各工會自定人數門檻，8成工會達標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">罷課公投</span><br />\n條件1:<br />\n全港10000名中學生參與公投。<br />\n條件2:<br />\n六成人支持罷課行動。<br />\n<br />\n若同時達成2個條件，就會啓動聯合三罷計劃！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yg5HowK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYg5HowK.jpg&h=8fbbcae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聯合三罷計劃：</span></ins><br />\n第一階段：<br />\n- 3日警示式罷工，可以用各方式加入罷工，例如SL...AL...bababa<br />\n<br />\n第二階段：<br />\n- 真三罷<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>Q&amp;A時間：</ins></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：現時工會人數幾多？6萬人死線係幾時？</span><br />\nA：23個工會會員人數近1萬，要6萬人其實唔係冇機會，大家記唔記得2月初醫護罷工？當時HAEA嘅會員人數兩星期內由1000左右增加到20000人，係HA嘅四份之一員工！死線係公投當日！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：罷工有無保障？</span><br />\nA :  政治罷工法例無保障，所以人數越多保障越大，夠多人佢冇可能炒哂你哋！呢個亦都係點解罷工前要搞公投！工會會提供一切法律/資金支援！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：唔夠6萬係咪會提早失敗？公投會唔會犯限聚令？</span><br />\nA :  公投日亦會招收會員，不會宣佈提早失敗。公投除咗表態是否罷工，亦向國際社會表達民意。公投會分流，實體投票，票站多於一個。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>結語：</ins></span></span></div><br />\n大三罷係反對國安法嘅最後機會，請各位手足團結一次！<br />\n<br />\n知道大家對三罷冇咩信心，但今次同9.2 9.3 11.11 嘅三罷係好大分別！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次三罷係由工會/學生組織發起，並且有公投作為人數保證，效果係前所未有！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有睇新聞都知，政府今日發咗篇聲明，瘋狂狙擊個公投。正所謂敵人反對嘅我哋更加要做，大家快啲spread個公投出去！！"},{"pid":"8c5fdacf0b364b14e9af86a3a5862a5014ad59e5","tid":2060447,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aH3qUBz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaH3qUBz.jpg&h=6d301a53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRhfxof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRhfxof.jpg&h=cb453c15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdf86ea36b9d8027ca090bfd09bf213e1e7d5d8c","tid":2060447,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91734cd5f5d762682a5ebf807588e09f1e7904ce","tid":2060447,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11727dc4389e4c8677562b5458e3cf2f87db3dae","tid":2060447,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a90edfcd20ba569b41d35543ce182782d43284","tid":2060447,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"今個星期日投票<br />\n<br />\n未做工會會員既可以即時入會， 然後參與投票。"},{"pid":"b831476176a8e509392d9a2d5cc924236a11ef61","tid":2060447,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4fb7fec309ac23f9aa0ebaae3a7c4e660730b9","tid":2060447,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979349f7632f0c4c936c95eaf59a0